                    <persName>Yeshūa' bar Phetion</persName>.</desc>
              </handNote>
              <handNote medium="unknown" xml:id="handNote2" scope="minor" script="syr">
                <desc>Part of a prayer for the Commemoration of <persName>Bar-saumā</persName>,
                  written in a rude hand of later date.</desc>
              </handNote>
              <handNote medium="unknown" xml:id="handNote3" scope="minor" script="syr">
